277
00:14:20,740 --> 00:14:24,100
♪I keep waiting for you under the light♪

278
00:14:24,100 --> 00:14:31,140
♪After hesitating, I finally find the courage
to light up your heart and stay with you♪

279
00:14:53,200 --> 00:14:57,680
♪That damaged but peaceful,
little dream♪

280
00:14:57,920 --> 00:15:02,080
♪Unintentionally shines into my life
through the window♪

281
00:15:02,200 --> 00:15:06,200
♪You never said it,
and I never mention it♪

282
00:15:06,440 --> 00:15:09,480
