283
00:15:10,160 --> 00:15:14,560
♪Because of you, my world becomes blurry♪

284
00:15:14,760 --> 00:15:18,680
♪One step forward and back,
I keep guessing your feeling♪

285
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:22,760
♪You never understood
this feelings that came out of nowhere♪

286
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:25,080
♪Under your control♪

287
00:15:25,360 --> 00:15:27,040
♪I want to say♪

288
00:15:27,320 --> 00:15:30,720
♪Will you care about
my feelings once again♪

289
00:15:31,160 --> 00:15:35,400
♪Will you let me walk on your heart
in the middle of the night♪

290
00:15:35,520 --> 00:15:38,520
♪I dare not think too much♪

291
00:15:38,640 --> 00:15:43,560
♪Or ask that you prove your love to me♪

292
00:15:43,720 --> 00:15:47,680
♪Will you also hold onto your phone,
waiting for me sometimes♪

293
00:15:48,280 --> 00:15:52,360
♪Are the songs you shared about me♪

294
00:15:52,640 --> 00:15:55,600
♪I dare not say too much♪

295
00:15:55,600 --> 00:15:59,480
♪Maybe you already understand♪

296
00:15:59,920 --> 00:16:02,120
♪My heart♪
